    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>A 5-foot-diameter &amp;Reference[sphere]{sphere} of &amp;Reference[fire]{fire} appears in an unoccupied space of your choice within range and lasts for the duration. Any creature that ends its turn within 5 feet of the &amp;Reference[sphere]{sphere} must make a &amp;Reference[dex]{Dexterity} saving throw. The creature takes 2d6 &amp;Reference[fire]{fire} damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p>As a bonus action, you can move the &amp;Reference[sphere]{sphere} up to 30 feet. If you ram the &amp;Reference[sphere]{sphere} into a creature, that creature must make the saving throw against the sphere's damage, and the &amp;Reference[sphere]{sphere} stops moving this turn.</p>\n<p>When you move the &amp;Reference[sphere]{sphere}, you can direct it over barriers up to 5 feet tall and jump it across pits up to 10 feet wide. The &amp;Reference[sphere]{sphere} ignites flammable objects not being worn or carried, and it sheds bright light in a 20-foot radius and dim light for an additional 20 feet.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 2nd.</p>\n</div>",
